title: Kenya-based aquaculture tech Victory Farms nets $5M funding to expand into new markets - TechCrunch
content: Kenya-based aquaculture tech Victory Farms nets $5M funding to expand into new markets  TechCrunch
description: Victory Farms, an aquaculture startup and farm for tilapia fish comprising hatcheries, nursery ponds and deep-water cages, has raised $5 million in new funding.
